REQUIREMENTS:

- Ocaml v4.01 or later.
  Note that some package managers have slow to pick up this release.
  It is available from http://caml.inria.fr/ocaml/release.en.html.
  You can find the version of your release using 'ocamlc -v'.
- LLVM 3.4 or later.
- Ocaml-LLVM bindings.

INSTALLATION:

Type make in the main folder.
This produces several binaries:

./iplc      The iplc compiler.
./iplc.opt  An optimized version of the iplc compiler.
./iplctop   An Ocaml toplevel with iplc preloaded.
